data.description: Nestled in the coveted Southmoor neighborhood of Overland Park, the charm and character of this 2 story blissful cottage-style home on 0.69 acres, with 166ft OF STREET FRONT, will make you fall in love! The home is set back from Walmer St, giving the feel of privacy while being nearby shopping, entertainment, and more offered at The Shops of Prairie Village. Enter the cozy front hall to the beautiful hardwood/tiled first floor. Enjoy cozy evenings in the spacious and bright hearth room, or in the den (converted from a third bedroom - easily able to be converted back with the addition of doors). This home's dining room is to die for, with its four HUGE picture windows overlooking a fabulous 460 sqft. all-seasons patio room, perfect for anything from quiet time to family gatherings or extra entertaining space. Bring your good taste and creativity and capitalize on all the character of the natural slate stone floor in the kitchen, breakfast and sunroom areas. Exit through the back door into the meticulously cared for shaded back garden, complete with garden shed. You'll love watching the plant life come alive all around your new property through the seasons, attracting all types of animal life and butterflies. Finally, the second floor primary bedroom/bathroom screams endless possibilities for your private, high-class getaway space, right at home. This home also offers abundant built-in storage spaces and a large basement. The basement is equipped with a built in bar/game area, 4th non-conforming bedroom, 1/2 bathroom and large laundry room/workshop. Come explore this one of a kind home today!
